---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Quench Thirst with Dew — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Quench Thirst with Dew</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">UFO Art Gallery | 2023</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>Presents work from two collaborating artists exploring hybrid forms and experimental approaches. Szostek displays post-body installations using her signature "skin" technique, while Biber showcases abstract collage paintings and textiles that blend organic elements with "technological and constructivist brutalism to create a Romantic vision of a post-world." Both artists employ digital and material art convergence, engaging in "re-analogizing"—deconstructing and remixing internet imagery. Their practice interrogates contemporary cultural production to reveal "primal motifs, tribal and universal symbols."</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Artists:</strong> Agnieszka Szostek, Michael Biber</p>
      <p><strong>Curator:</strong> Michalina Sablik</p>
      <p><strong>Translation:</strong> Piotr Mierzwa</p>
      <p><strong>Photography:</strong> Szymon Soko&#322;owski</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
